{
  "texts": [
    "In this case there exist two layers i 1 and i 2 (not necessarily distinct) such that",
    "with the convention that L 0 = L κ and L κ+1 = L 1.",
    "There are γ edges between L i1-1 and one node of V cyc,k in L i1.",
    "Similarly, there are γ edges between L i2+1 and one node of V cyc,k in L i2.",
    "Since κ ≥ 3, these edges are distinct and we deduce |E ↑ cyc,k | ≥ 2γ."
  ]
}